data.description: This delightful home features three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a two-car attached garage. As you approach the house, you're greeted by a charming front porch that leads you into this inviting residence. Upon entering, you find yourself in the front living room, which can serve as a cozy secondary living space or a potential office. Moving forward, you'll discover a beautiful fireplace and a second living area. The area between the second living space and the kitchen is well-suited for a dining area. Sliding doors in the kitchen open up to the back patio and a level backyard. The bedrooms are all generously sized and come with spacious bathrooms. As a bonus, there's an unfinished basement. This home is a fantastic find in a superb location.
